      "text": [
        "هِ بَوْلٌ لاَ يَقْدِرُ عَلَى غَسْلِهِ قَالَ «يُصَلِّي فِيهِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.752 - Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Halabi asked Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) about a man who has only one garment, and it has urine on it, but he is unable to wash it.\nImam (as) said: \"He should pray in it.\""
        ]
      }
